          "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Antineutrophil Cytoplasmic Antibodies (ANCA).</span></span></span></p>"
